imdb.plot outline: Daily Dab TV is an online show dedicated to covering the latest in Cannabis News, Culture, Music and Entertainment. Stay tuned and watch our weekly broadcasts, browse through our online gallery of photos from events and festivals that you were either at or wish you had went to! We basically travel the country and do cool stuff- while also plugging the new up and coming businesses in the Cannabis, Music and Entertainment industry.
